Name: Parking Attendant
About the game: Parking Attendant is an arcade game with a top view, where the player has to Park the car and collect all the stars, avoiding obstacles. There are several types of obstacles - oil puddle on the road, a huge hole where your car can fall. Also there is a possibility of puncturing the tires, then it becomes very difficult to control your car! The game is suitable for children.
